InterationalOrder - Class in Onlinehandel.entities
An international order within the Onlinehandel.

For international orders a factor can be set that is used to calculate customs when crossing borders.

This factor is applied to the items' total value when calculating the total of an international order.

InterationalOrder(long, Costumer, Iterable<Item>) - Constructor for class Onlinehandel.entities.InterationalOrder
Constructs an international order with specified id, costumer and at least one item.
The id must be greater than 0 and the reference type arguments must be non-null.
When invalid arguments are passed an IllegalArgumentException is thrown.
